<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Make request to table with column named 0 (zero).</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$cols = array('col', '0', '1', '2', );
$select = $table-&gt;select();
$select-&gt;from($table, $cols);
echo $select-&gt;__toString();
</code></pre>

<p>Expected:
SELECT <code>table_name</code>.<code>col</code>, <code>table_name</code>.<code>0</code>, <code>table_name</code>.<code>1</code>, <code>table_name</code>.<code>2</code> FROM <code>table_name</code>
Actual:
SELECT <code>table_name</code>.<code>col</code>, <code>table_name</code>.<code>1</code>, <code>table_name</code>.<code>2</code> FROM <code>table_name</code></p>

<p>There is no column named <code>0</code> in request, but should be.</p>

<p>Column filtered in class Zend_Db_Select, function _tableCols().</p>

